OL,3,CThe train station frozen in time
OL,4,Cthat's now up for auction
OL,6,FJust over a week from now, this place
OL,7,Fgoes under the auctioneer's hammer.
OL,9,FGuide price, #35,000-40,000 - and then
OL,10,Fyou'll need to ask for planning
OL,11,Fpermission if you fancy a quirky but
OL,12,Felegant home, and the phone numbers of
OL,13,Fseveral good builders.
