OL,3,CThe train station frozen in time
OL,4,Cthat's now up for auction
OL,6,FBut if those are the drawbacks - well,
OL,7,Fyou do get several waiting rooms with
OL,8,Fwooden shelves and elegant fireplaces,
OL,9,Fsolid brick walls, elegant windows,
OL,10,Flong benches and - one thing that's
OL,11,Fvery hard to recreate on telly - a
OL,12,Funique and evocative scent, a
OL,13,Fcombination of lamp oil and grass
OL,14,Fcuttings and time.
OL,16,FMelfyn Williams, who will auction
OL,17,FPentre Berw's station off next week,
OL,18,Ftells us you never quite know what'll
OL,19,Fhappen once a lot comes up - but it
OL,20,Fisn't actually the first railway
OL,21,Fstation he has sold in his career.
