OL,3,CThe train station frozen in time
OL,4,Cthat's now up for auction
OL,6,FAs we wander from waiting room to
OL,7,Fwaiting room - still in the old London
OL,8,Fand North Western Railway colours - it
OL,9,Fdoesn't take much to imagine what this
OL,10,Fplace was like when the smoke and the
OL,11,Fsteam and the passengers were here.
OL,13,FSo, all those fireplaces - marble in
OL,14,Fthe waiting room, cast iron in the
OL,15,Fstaff bit - might find themselves a
OL,16,Fnew flame: whoever buys this is buying
OL,17,Fan atmosphere you can't entirely get
OL,18,Ffrom just seeing the catalogue or the
OL,19,Fpictures.
