OL,3,CThe train station frozen in time
OL,4,Cthat's now up for auction
OL,6,FIt's a perfect time capsule, a place
OL,7,Fwhere the trains stopped running but
OL,8,Fthe scent of the past still finds you
OL,9,F- a passenger on an empty platform,
OL,10,Fwhere your imagination takes a journey
OL,11,Finstead.
